  <text>
    <body>
  <div type="scene" n="1">
    <head>SCENE II.</head>
    <stage type='personnages'><app>
        <lem wit="#C #D #E">JOCASTE, ANTIGONE, OLYMPE. </lem>
        <rdg wit="#A #B">IOCASTE, ANTIGONE, OLYMPE. </rdg>
      </app></stage>
    <sp>
      <speaker><app>
        <lem wit="#C #D #E">Jocaste. </lem>
        <rdg wit="#A #B">Iocaste. </rdg>
      </app></speaker>
<l n="39">
MA 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #E">Fille, </lem>
        <rdg wit="#B #C #D">Fille </rdg>
      </app>

      <app>
        <lem wit="#C #D #E">avez&#160;vous </lem>
        <rdg wit="#A">auez&#160;vous </rdg>
        <rdg wit="#B">avez-vous </rdg>
      </app>
sçeu l’excez de nos 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #E">miseres. </lem>
        <rdg wit="#B #C #D">miseres&#160;? </rdg>
      </app>
</l>

    </sp>
    <sp>
      <speaker><app>
        <lem wit="#A #C #D #E">ANTIGONE. </lem>
        <rdg wit="#B">ANTIGONE, </rdg>
      </app></speaker>
<l n="40">

      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #C #E">Oüy, </lem>
        <rdg wit="#D">Ouy, </rdg>
      </app>
Madame, on m’a dit la fureur de mes freres. </l>

    </sp>
    <sp>
      <speaker><app>
        <lem wit="#C #D #E">JOCASTE. </lem>
        <rdg wit="#A #B">IOCASTE. </rdg>
      </app></speaker>
<l n="41">
      <app>
        <lem wit="#E">Allons, chere Antigone, allons tout de ce pas,</lem>
        <rdg wit="#A">Allons, chere Antigone, allons tout de ce pas,</rdg>
        <rdg wit="#B">Allons, chere Antigone, allons tout de ce pas,</rdg>
        <rdg wit="#C">Allons, chere Antigone, allons tout de ce pas,</rdg>
        <rdg wit="#D">Allons, chere Antigone, &amp; courons de ce pas,</rdg>
      </app>
</l>

<l n="42">
Arrester s’il se peut leur parricide 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #E">bras, </lem>
        <rdg wit="#B #C #D">bras. </rdg>
      </app>
</l>

<l n="43">
Allons leur faire voir ce qu’ils ont de plus tendre&#160;; </l>

<l n="44">
Voyons si contre nous ils pourront se défendre, </l>

<l n="45">
Ou s’ils oseront bien dans leur noire 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #E">fureur </lem>
        <rdg wit="#B #C #D">fureur, </rdg>
      </app>
</l>

<l n="46">

      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #E">Respandre </lem>
        <rdg wit="#B">Repandre </rdg>
        <rdg wit="#C #D">Répandre </rdg>
      </app>
nostre sang pour attaquer le leur. </l>

    </sp>
    <sp>
      <speaker>ANTIGONE.</speaker>
<l n="47">
Madame, c’en est fait, 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #D #E">voicy </lem>
        <rdg wit="#C">voici </rdg>
      </app>
le Roy 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #E">luy&#160;mesme. </lem>
        <rdg wit="#B">luy-mesme. </rdg>
        <rdg wit="#C">lui-mesme. </rdg>
        <rdg wit="#D">lui-même. </rdg>
      </app>
</l>

</sp>
</div>
